{"tid":878300,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[爭咩丫，溝埋黎做牛河漢堡丫，笨！]霆鋒研製新漢堡：想過出牛河味","createTime":"2018-10-27T04:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T11:04:27.000Z","uid":47132,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8190792d918c542c0893fc17730c3d466d949a0e","tid":878300,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sc1.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201304/12018_10151583031926154_996601348_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsc1.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201304%2F12018_10151583031926154_996601348_n.jpg&h=f9439425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝霆鋒與大型連鎖快餐店合作推出漢堡包，25日出席宣傳活動。霆鋒化身Chef Le Mon大展廚藝，即席炮製新款漢堡包，他表示今次花了很多心機研製出兩款港式風味漢堡包，此外還有薯條、飲品同雪糕，他直言試驗了很多個月，期間有很多黐線想法，因想挑戰極限，乾炒牛河味都有諗過，希望再有機會突破。<br />\n<br />\n問到有否找身邊人試食？霆鋒說沒有，因過程機密，無人知亦無人見到。會否帶兩個仔去試？他說：「遲一些先，再說吧。」霆鋒又笑言研製這新系列食物，令他肥了少許，因要不斷試食：「每日食很多個包，肯定人生一日內最多。」霆鋒表示選用的都是高級食材和醬料，絕非垃圾食物。"},{"pid":"f676662d4c0e3b4b17913fc469c556a6e530fd72","tid":878300,"uid":122233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">霆鋒表示選用的都是高級食材和醬料，絕非垃圾食物。</span><br />\n<br />\n可惜溝埋一齊變左垃圾食物都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3ea8e257ca1aa61fafb8bd98f0889ecb6a04f4","tid":878300,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd918d9457886016690b0d02df0fccb217ca79d","tid":878300,"uid":51639,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"係麥當勞講高級食材 笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa72700f9ee72eae838770657a505ba4a6d601ac","tid":878300,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r